156
00:12:31,667 --> 00:12:33,267
Oo.

157
00:12:39,033 --> 00:12:45,200
Sabi ko sa'yo... Sabi ko sa'yo hindi ako 'yon.

158
00:12:47,133 --> 00:12:52,500
Paulit-ulit kong sinasabing inosente ako. Pero bakit...

159
00:12:53,900 --> 00:12:56,367
Dapat nagtiwala ka sa akin noon.

160
00:12:56,367 --> 00:12:59,533
Bakit ngayon pa ito binabanggit?

161
00:12:59,533 --> 00:13:00,533
Pasensya na.

162
00:13:00,533 --> 00:13:03,733
Pinabuhay mo akong parang mamamatay-tao
nang mahigit tatlumpung taon,

163
00:13:03,733 --> 00:13:07,200
