Dapat hinayaan mo na lang akong
mabuhay nang hindi ko alam.

174
00:14:05,967 --> 00:14:07,667
Pasensya na...

175
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:15,000
Pasensya na talaga.

176
00:14:20,433 --> 00:14:23,167
